doctor.name: Dr. Arman Uddin Ahmad
doctor.info: Dr. Arman Uddin Ahmad is a Eye Specialist in Kushtia. His qualification is MBBS, FCPS (EYE), MS (EYE). He is a Assistant Professor, Eye at Kushtia Medical College & Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Sono Consultation Center, Kushtia. Practicing hour of Dr. Arman Uddin Ahmad at Sono Consultation Center, Kushtia is 5pm to 8pm (Sat, Mon, Wed).

chamber.address: Sono Tower 2, Court Para, Kushtia, Bangladesh
